{"published time": "2024-03-28T03:33:45+08:00", "images": ["https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23-1024x680.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1-1024x669.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1024x680.jpg"], "content": "<div class=\"el-single-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2.jpg 1280w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2-300x162.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2-1024x552.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2-768x414.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2-60x32.jpg 60w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"690\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-2.jpg\" width=\"1280\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n <p>\n  On the morning of March 20, 2023, a public hearing was held in the municipality of Barra do Corda convened by the Barra do Corda Rural Workers Union and the Family Farmers Association of Fazenda S\u00e3o Francisco to denounce the crimes of the latifundal The life of the peasants of the S\u00e3o Francisco Camp, located in the Carrasco village.\n </p>\n <p>\n  Peasant families suffer from the action of militias and gunmen at the behest of land grary landowners. The conflict in Barra do Corda gained national projection at the end of last year when a group of gunmen was ambushed\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/ma-emboscada-contra-grupo-pistoleiro-empenhado-em-despejo-ilegal-revela-presenca-massiva-de-policiais-no-bando/\">\n   during an attempted illegal eviction in the village Carrasco, which resulted in the death of a military police officer\n  </a>\n  .\n </p>\n <p>\n  As a form of retaliation, two peasants were murdered, Adonias Fernandes da Silva and Francisco Pereira da Silva Filho. In a support note to the S\u00e3o Francisco camping peasants published on March 13, 2024, the Solidarity Committee for the Fight for the Land (Comsolute) states: \u201cAll propaganda that the peasants were killed in confrontation is the attempted Secretariat of Public Security to mask the fact that there was a gang of active and retirees police that would massacreate the peasants to secure the land for the land grabbers. \u201d\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171610\" data-id=\"171610\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23-1024x680.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23-300x199.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23-768x510.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23-60x40.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23.jpg 1280w\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"680\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23-1024x680.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-23-1024x680.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171609\" data-id=\"171609\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1-1024x669.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1-1024x669.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1-300x196.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1-768x502.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1-60x39.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1.jpg 1280w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"669\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1-1024x669.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1-1024x669.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171605\" data-id=\"171605\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1024x680.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-300x199.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-768x510.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-60x40.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24.jpg 1280w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"680\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1024x680.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/PHOTO-2024-03-21-22-16-24-1024x680.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  The peasants in struggle of the village vilela, from the municipality of Junco do Maranh\u00e3o, even traveled Barra do Corda to be present at the hearing as a demonstration of solidarity and example that the consequent union and peasant organization is able to gain great victories. In addition to the participation of the vilela village, students of the Student Collective Children of the People were present and a member of the Com -Solute who have remembered at all times in their interventions that the peasants in Barra do Corda are not alone in their fight and that they will disclose what is occurring to break the attempted criminalization and isolation untied by the press in Maranh\u00e3o.\n </p>\n</div>", "pdf_content": null, "pdf_links": [], "source": "https://anovademocracia.com.br/ma-camponeses-de-barra-do-corda-realizam-audiencia-publica-para-denunciar-crimes-do-latifundio/", "type": "article", "title": "MA: Barra do Corda peasants hold a public hearing to denounce Latifundium crimes - the new democracy", "description": "Peasant families suffer from the action of militias and gunmen at the behest of land grary landowners.", "modified time": "2024-03-27T16:33:49-03:00", "updated time": "2024-03-27T16:33:49-03:00", "author": ["Comit\u00ea de Apoio 